{"tid":1832440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[大整合]我要前線BB安全返屋企！","createTime":"2020-01-21T07:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T08:59:55.000Z","uid":211994,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"484ab3f59d1d2fc3dcbd27306c9019b1233f95fd","tid":1832440,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:25:33.000Z","msg":"可能香城Online已經營運咗7個月，大部分手足都已經選擇好哂自己嘅定位，對於自己崗位同職責都有好深入嘅了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係，作為兵種危險程度較高嘅前線，人員替換嘅情況好高，比起裝備同飯券，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線最缺嘅係人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但偏偏，最近可以比前線學習嘅資源都好缺乏，令到一啲想轉職業嘅手足無處入手，結果喺仲未掌握竅門前就比綠色曱甴KO咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔想手足喺未裝備好自己嘅情況下，成就唔到任何野就犧牲咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以以下我會整合下部分我認為有用嘅資訊，供各位想升級嘅和理勇、後排參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦希望咁多位老手溫故知新，同時幫小弟鑑別下我搵嘅資料會否過時或者唔齊全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非常感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裝備：</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n職業安全眼罩, 專業選購指南 by 無名博士 (買眼罩前必定要睇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360818</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8.13 高階護目鏡更新 (有平有貴) &amp; 四眼仔新方法 (重開)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8.20 dgx 防割手套,袖,頸巾,電筒 &amp;全防具圖鑑 唔該大家買裝俾連偎牆巴絲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489603</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴防具攻略更新 7093可接502蓋!! 裝修又想身體健康必入 (連購買link)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384250</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n前海豹部隊教你如何將隨身物品變為自衞武器<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n保護自己，全民VPN！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1819200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1819200</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戰術 戰略 及技巧：</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【戰術】【快做仆街仔】大量珍藏流出！新年送大禮！！勁過除夕抽獎！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1808752</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地已經冇曬戰術可以用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1816267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1816267</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">以上兩篇係我搵到較為更新嘅資料，以下嘅可以頂住檔，但唔好盡信</span><br />\n<br />\n[戰術]兵種分工，戰術布陣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[關於地下化] 勇武小隊肯接受全部小隊已被監視未？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824921</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全民自學- 十秒內全滅催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343743</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">訓練：</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成為特警的體能要求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810118</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫我入黎推到所有手足做體能！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810496</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zQPTCo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zQPTCo.png&h=06b6ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">心態：</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[剖析前線心態] 發夢做過前線，同你講下點解前線唔肯散，同點先可以令前線散<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402304</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n依場運動其實有個問題好耐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">返屋企：</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[FB轉] 今日荔枝角和你LUNCH有便衣狗跟蹤 再次證明反跟蹤嘅重要性<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1827951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1827951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[保平安] 反跟蹤方法，做足先好出門口<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1686614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1686614</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【戰術整合POST】D狗開始散水後跟蹤人啦 反跟蹤學定救命！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其他需知事項：</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李安然大律師教你被捕後面對警察的「救命招」 (文字版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以一齊返屋企。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632e48a158e78b391a3110a3d579e10c5ae234d1","tid":1832440,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"Repeat after me：裝備好自己 安全返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3436ce97ea8427680b169da138d84e8c451aaf47","tid":1832440,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"裝備好自己 安全返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4e5a2615667aa66f51b8db70324cd5e203b34d","tid":1832440,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"裝備好自己 安全返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1862d296e8d7ea8b1870397dfe8327eef7bf372","tid":1832440,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:26:52.000Z","msg":"裝備好自己 安全返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f8494d96d6515339469f1216b026d801e7cd59","tid":1832440,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"裝備好自己 安全返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9668b1ed44b51489dd633de342d1e2fe90d3c2a9","tid":1832440,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"裝備好自己 安全返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b4450878c78155b2c13ab6d17f61bfbe540de8","tid":1832440,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-